<BaseLayout title="Cubby — Know Where Everything Lives" description="Cubby helps you keep track of everything you own — across homes, rooms, closets, and storage spaces. A calm, beautiful home inventory app for iOS.">
  <section class="hero"><img class="app-icon" src="/app-icon.png" alt="Cubby app icon" /><h1>Cubby</h1><p class="tagline">Know where everything lives.</p><a class="app-store-badge" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6751732388" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://tools.applemediaservices.com/api/badges/download-on-the-app-store/black/en-us?size=250x83" alt="Download on the App Store" /></a><div class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg></div></section>
  <section class="section features"><h2 class="section-title fade-in">Everything in its place</h2><div class="feature-grid"><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">📦</div><h3>Nested Storage</h3><p>Organize the way your stuff actually lives — homes, rooms, closets, shelves, boxes. As deep as you need.</p></div><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">🔍</div><h3>Smart Search</h3><p>Find anything across all your spaces instantly. No more wondering which closet your winter coat is in.</p></div><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">📸</div><h3>Photo Organization</h3><p>Snap a photo so you remember exactly what's in that box in the garage. Visual inventory, effortless.</p></div><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">☁️</div><h3>iCloud Sync</h3><p>Your inventory stays in sync across all your devices. Add items on your phone, check from your iPad.</p></div><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">🏠</div><h3>Multiple Homes</h3><p>Cabin, apartment, storage unit, parents' garage — track it all in one place, across every location.</p></div><div class="feature-card fade-in"><div class="feature-icon">✨</div><h3>Calm Design</h3><p>No clutter, no complexity. Just a simple, beautiful interface that stays out of your way.</p></div></div></section>
  <section class="section how"><h2 class="section-title fade-in">Think in nesting boxes</h2><div class="breadcrumb-demo fade-in"><span>🏠 Home</span><span class="arrow">→</span><span>Bedroom Closet</span><span class="arrow">→</span><span>Top Shelf</span><span class="arrow">→</span><span>Blue Box</span></div><p class="caption fade-in">Cubby mirrors how you actually store things. Drill down to find exactly what you're looking for — or search to jump straight there.</p></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="section-inner"><p class="section-kicker">Guides</p><h2 class="section-title">Start with a system, not a junk drawer with ambition.</h2><p class="section-copy">The new Cubby blog has practical guides for home inventories, moving boxes, emergency kits, storage bins, and all the other places household sanity goes to die.</p><p class="section-copy"><a href="/blog">Read the Cubby blog →</a></p></div></section>
  <section class="cta"><h2 class="fade-in">Stop losing things</h2><p class="fade-in">Free on the App Store. Your stuff will thank you.</p><a class="app-store-badge fade-in" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6751732388" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://tools.applemediaservices.com/api/badges/download-on-the-app-store/black/en-us?size=250x83" alt="Download on the App Store" /></a></section>
</BaseLayout>
